'''Imix''' ({{Pronounce|Y|miks|refs={{Cite dragon/93/Ay pronunseeAYshun gyd|26}}}}) was the evil [[archomental]] of fire. He was a [[primordial]] older than the world itself.<ref> 

Imix's many nicknames and titles included the '''Prince of Elemental Evil''', the '''All-Consuming Fire''', and the '''Eternal Flame'''.
{{Quote|Someday, there will be only fire. Someday, everything will burn.|Imix}}
